{"tid":895893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[讚嘆] MAMAMOO實力猛到網友跪了","createTime":"2018-11-09T14:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T19:00:42.000Z","uid":74065,"like":29,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cdef992dc872c151e34c9bb4d5f683208fcf7eda","tid":895893,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"南韓「吞CD實力」女團MAMAMOO由頌樂、玟星、輝人及華莎組成，4人皆有著出眾的歌喉、，以現場完美的演唱闖出名聲，音源表現更是稱霸排行榜。她們日前在日本音樂節目《power of k》live演唱實力震撼全場，有頻道更是直接貼出「MR版」（music removed），4人零破綻的歌喉，聽得歌迷直呼起雞皮疙瘩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JigxgpI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJigxgpI.jpg&h=6d8e217f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼MAMAMOO每位成員都很會唱。（圖／翻攝自UNICORN TV Youtube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pVZwYka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpVZwYka.jpg&h=5f2453a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMAMAMOO日前出演日本音樂節目《power of k》宣傳新歌《Egotistic》，4人都拿著手麥唱歌，才剛開口就讓人起雞皮疙瘩，且她們全程開全麥唱跳，連過程中的高音伴奏都實力演出，完全零失誤，呈現出如同在聽CD般的音色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ubGhIPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FubGhIPj.jpg&h=655ea5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼MAMAMOO每次的現場演出都讓人驚艷。（圖／翻攝自UNICORN TV Youtube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wTCOfQT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwTCOfQT.jpg&h=b667fffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMAMAMOO出道以來就以實力唱將廣為人知，不過，這場Live演出獲得高度評價，網友紛紛<br />\n讚美「再聽一次還是覺得猛」，還有人直呼「她們不是偶像，是4個歌手」、「連伴奏都<br />\n能唱得跟CD一樣」、「實力真的很好」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-L34g6zhA_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-L34g6zhA_4&d=SNJlKeDMB3Z0KcbjhlF8%2Fmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=49f84525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-L34g6zhA_4</a><br />\n<br />\n班妹妹D應援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMAMAMOO準備又CB啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c4696d7adc12186a5a8d88ab1e057e943064ce","tid":895893,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p283S7n_Qew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp283S7n_Qew&d=SNJlKeDMB3Z0KcbjhlF8%2Fmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9c6d0554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p283S7n_Qew</a><br />\n放錯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfc46f919de2c4193674cd2605556bb4a228e18","tid":895893,"uid":213300,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"izone都屌打mamamoo啦<br />\n都唔使用大boss twice"},{"pid":"47370d19fbdcd55488742798726f05849e5a14e8","tid":895893,"uid":35756,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你拎mamamoo同隊垃圾比無意思咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa180757392b41ead0bb1e9ce84371e1908b1f2","tid":895893,"uid":10290,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"樓主又陰d隂d踩鳩twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67776bf8c879f1851067a3741b03c8841feea78f","tid":895893,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fa180757392b41ead0bb1e9ce84371e1908b1f2","tid":895893,"uid":10290,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:34:19.000Z","msg":"樓主又陰d隂d踩鳩tw