援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMAMAMOO準備又CB啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"尼個放錯片有少少。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944e5e9ad54b3896ec3b6fb7fa78620244d58fe8","tid":895893,"uid":139671,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"47370d19fbdcd55488742798726f05849e5a14e8","tid":895893,"uid":35756,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你拎mamamoo同隊垃圾比無意思咖喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n啲3.4線團or暗團分分鐘有大部分實力好過佢地"},{"pid":"2bf1c88613b83feacf9495d7f141a89dd9f87d57","tid":895893,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"開口跪了"}]}